::Cygnar::
    It was over.  The base was gone.  He flew down immediately and began 
digging at the crumbled rock.  He knew he'd need help.  He sent a com to 
Like-Like assuming that he had never gotten back.  "Like-Like.  This is 
Cygnar.  I think we may be the only Destrons left here.  Come back to base we 
must start to rebuild for when Mag... er ...Master returns."
